Class MainApp

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
fraus.javaproject.MainApp
public class MainApp
extends javafx.application.Application
JavaFX Main application, contains all of the view method to display the root page, dialog, and other pages. This application uses Model-View-Controller pattern to the efficiently display information to users.
